          Not all registered agent services are created equal. Here are the key factors to consider when choosing a provider:
        </p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-3">
          <li>
            <strong>Pricing and transparency.</strong> Look at both the first-year cost and the ongoing renewal rate. Some services lure you in with a free first year but charge significantly more upon renewal. Make sure you understand the long-term cost.
